{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":64681,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"哇我好喜欢看不见的城市，表面上很天马行空细品之下又非常有隐喻和逻辑","timestamp":1593443913,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":64687,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"寒冬夜行人还没看完，感觉就是天才写书的风格）","timestamp":1593443966,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":64697,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"是 天 才\n老实说飘这个字缺少感觉...感觉dz可以先去把现代派都看一遍（","timestamp":1593444020,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":64712,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"寒冬夜行人看的电子版，看到一半我以为是盗版的随便找了几本书拼一起了","timestamp":1593444177,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":64723,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 我现在在看《如果在冬夜，一个旅人》，到目前为止每一章节的逻辑关系都不是很明确，不过每一章节的情节都很有意思hh好久没有看这种偏严肃一点的文学了，以前都是剧情流小说看的多，所以看这个还有丢丢不适应TAT打算下一本看 看不见的城市！","timestamp":1593444276,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":64725,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"一度沉迷树上的男爵 年少时期甚至放肆仿写（x","timestamp":1593444281,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":64735,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 飘就是对应形容以前看的很“实”的小说啦😂之前没接触过这种类型的书～所以想听听了解多的人有什么样的感觉","timestamp":1593444387,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":64740,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"看了看不见的城市，实话说绝大部分内容看不太懂，觉得像词藻堆砌","timestamp":1593444455,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":64755,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 诶，寒冬夜行人另一个译名是不是《如果在冬夜，一个旅人》hh那确实，每章都是新故事，不过你这个感觉是不是和主角的感受一样了～","timestamp":1593444606,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":64759,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 我就是要强迫自己集中注意力才看的进去😂","timestamp":1593444642,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":65026,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 我觉得寒冬夜行人超好看！很有新意，而且很轻松愉快，但不是那种很浅薄的愉快。感觉卡尔维诺对很多事情看得很透彻，但是又很天真的感觉。","timestamp":1593447951,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":65029,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 求问现代派有什么比较推荐的书或者作家呢？","timestamp":1593448033,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":65056,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 艾略特 乔伊斯 马尔克斯 博尔赫斯 卡夫卡 里尔克 马雅可夫斯基....太多了 我觉得大部分作家都值得看2-3本以上 同期的超现实 象征主义 存在主义 荒诞派 意识流也都可一看（","timestamp":1593448452,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":65226,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 哇感谢！","timestamp":1593451238,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":65818,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":11013,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"轻盈、迅捷、准确、鲜明、繁复、结构","timestamp":1593484163,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":7,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":11013,"reply":15,"tag":null,"text":"最近在看卡尔维诺的书，感觉这种很“飘”的叙述方式好奇特哦（本人书看的少），有比较有心得体会的同学讲讲么～","timestamp":1593443836,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782585,"url":"","vote":{}}}